ertaining account. Dr KATHLEEN WALKER-MEIKLE gained her PhD at University College London.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCivilization, Medieval. 0aHuman-animal relationshipsxHistory. 0aPet ownerszEuropexHistoryyTo 1500. 0aPetszEuropexHistoryyTo 1500. 4aArt & Architecture. 4aMedieval History. 4aMedieval Literature. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh  aSquirrel.  adomesticity.  amonk.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBoydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package pre 2013z978311143139040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978178204040840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781782040408423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781782040408/original  a978-3-11-143139-0  Boydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package pre 2013b2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles